2Fact4hk.com%2Fpetition&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPi3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=622c026a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/petition</a></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">裡面有好多為香港打定安全網既聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假如我地唔打好 我地好難用<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">最低程度既損傷</span><br />\n去真正<span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港 奪權當家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></div><br />\n前一兩日李柱銘俾狗塔，但喺美國政壇引起如此大既迴響<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。正係<span style=\"color: gold;\">因為先前聯署同請求美帝落實《人權及民主法案》而致</span>，趁機<span style=\"color: teal;\">俾藉口美帝加速打殘狗共</span>，何樂不為<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Q&amp;A部分請㩒入去呢度<br />\n記得睇埋啊，好撚緊要啊</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">【偽 &middot; 正視聽】得啦我知我洗咗你地版<br />\n召喚聯署師長文Q&amp;A就放喺度啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1981260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1981260</a></span></div>"},{"pid":"6ceacba14eb938fadb87facab070148b98841242","tid":1980272,"uid":180634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:28:28.000Z","msg":"香港人是二等公民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f1fe2833c8fb94a31fe3520444bbdf8df119090","tid":1980272,"uid":86062,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:31:08.000Z","msg":"但如果大陸人唔抽，隻股都炒唔起<br />\n<br />\n利申：預左俾人屌"},{"pid":"2908859646076341900c2db94e02368d721745a7","tid":1980272,"uid":189374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f1fe2833c8fb94a31fe3520444bbdf8df119090","tid":1980272,"uid":86062,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:31:08.000Z","msg":"但如果大陸人唔抽，隻股都炒唔起<br />\n<br />\n利申：預左俾人屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime"