等於公開發售超額2倍，呢批一手黨就一定係毒瘤"},{"pid":"2be1dc3b214c1d1961c3ae56a60368d235ddd53b","tid":1980272,"uid":136994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2e700649b18855950d50135ff726c0d7cada9a97","tid":1980272,"uid":136994,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"5f1fe2833c8fb94a31fe3520444bbdf8df119090","tid":1980272,"uid":86062,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:31:08.000Z","msg":"但如果大陸人唔抽，隻股都炒唔起<br />\n<br />\n利申：預左俾人屌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:52:45.000Z","msg":"大陸人如果都只係用一人一戶方式抽，佢哋想中得多就唯有落大額孖展飛，呢一個情況之下一樣超額認購倍數多，但係起碼唔會玩爛A組，小散戶容易啲贏錢，舊年1530、1951未玩爛嘅時候超額唔算少，但係因為人頭少，要中就一啲都唔難。所以，佢哋落大額飛其實係利多於弊，可以令到超額倍數大增同時又唔會太影響散戶中籤率<br />\n<br />\n依家佢哋一人百戶，玩爛曬A組，結果小散戶贏錢機會大減，而一手黨即使有十萬廿萬人，都唔會令超額倍數大增，沛嘉嗰十幾萬一手黨其實只係相等於公開發售超額2倍，呢批一手黨就一定係毒瘤"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:55:01.000Z","msg":"B股股王6185仲要係100%中簽率，因為嗰陣人頭數唔多"},{"pid":"00695cf754585e628d4ce2a34e86e5e3bc1cf767","tid":1980272,"uid":210233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:59:46.000Z","msg":"我一月投訴過,証監只是noted with thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ffaba74f74f5c6db01f0d1b1b0cb22bb5295cd6","tid":1980272,"uid":268516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T06:01:01.000Z","msg":"啲股本身都係支那過黎昆人錢<br />\n俾番支那人無限抽其實無問題<br />\n支那人呃番支那人"},{"pid":"08caf9631459f08ababf7051a6fe2d7048b7b8a1","tid":1980272,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T06:02:58.000Z","msg":"証監<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0308039c96eea1ddad8874ec7ec09f5c22d6db73","tid":19